        <item>
            <title>【評測】PS5 Pro / PlayStation 5 Pro 詳細效能評測，實機遊戲 60fps 畫面 + 新光追效果放大睇 + 打機温度噪音</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/06/ps5-pro-review/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ps5-pro-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/06/ps5-pro-review/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 11:00:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[評測]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲評測]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PlayStation 5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1273358</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>PS5 Pro (PlayStation 5 Pro) 將於 11 月 7 日正式發售，新機引入更強處理晶片，帶來更強處理能力之餘，能夠保持細小的機身，確是非常吸引！但好多人都有疑惑，新機售價去到 $5,780，明顯是專門給對遊戲畫質、流暢度有追求的玩家而設，究竟是否適合自己去購買呢。而這些畫質、流暢度的變化，實際又是如何呢？今次我們就在發售之前，同大家介紹一下轉用 PS5 Pro 後獲得的各方面提升，給大家在選購之前作一個參考。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03524-1.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273616" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03524-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03524-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03524-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>自 PS5 推出以來，玩家都要在畫質與流暢度之間做出選擇。在 4K 解像度上想獲得更清晰、更多細節表現的畫面，無可避免犧牲遊戲流暢度；相反如用遊戲中的「效能模式」，雖然保持到 60 或接近 60fps 的流暢度，但遊戲清晰度就有明顯下降。PS5 Pro 就能給玩家既用到遊戲的高畫質模式，又同時能夠達到如 60fps 的流暢度。</p><p>PS5 Pro 採用更強勁的 GPU，比 PS5 在光線追蹤（Ray Tracing）的處理速度快了 2-3 倍，並引入全新 PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution (PSSR) 升級解像技術，帶來更精緻的畫面和流暢的遊戲體驗。我們將通過幾款熱門遊戲的實測結果，來看看 PS5 Pro 是否值得你考慮入手。</p><h2>外觀與設計</h2><p>首先我們來看看 PS5 Pro 的外觀特點，在之前的開箱文章也有介紹過，如果你已看過那篇文，可跳到下面遊戲評測部份。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03537-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273617" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03537-1-489x580.jpg" alt="" width="489" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03537-1-489x580.jpg 489w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03537-1.jpg 576w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 489px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03545-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273618" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03545-1-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03545-1-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03545-1.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p>PS5 Pro 的高度與 PS5 基本相同，但機身闊度縮小至與 PS5 Slim 一致。重量相比起 PS5 Slim 的 2.58kg，PS5 Pro 只增至 3.06 kg，如果同最初版本 PS5 的 4.48kg 比較的話，PS5 Pro 就顯得十分輕盈了，適合大家四處移動或搬到朋友家打機。對比初被 PS5，PS5 Pro 整體體積卻有所縮小，雖然高度、厚度未必會有好大分別，但機身闊度上就窄了很多。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03567.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273626" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03567-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03567-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03567.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲同 PS5 Slim 一樣，如果同初代 PS5 比較，機身闊度窄了很多</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03566-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273627" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03566-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03566-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03566-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲上圖左方 PS5 Pro, 右方初代 PS5</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03547-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273619" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03547-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03547-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03547-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>PS5 Pro 背面 USB 的排列與 PS5 Slim 版相似，同樣提供 2 個 10Gbps 傳輸速度的 USB Type-A 插口、LAN 與 HDMI 插口。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03550.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273620" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03550-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03550-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03550.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>如 PS5 Slim 版一樣機身表面提供兩個 USB-C 接口，其中一個支援連接 SSD 時獲得 10Gbps 速度，另一個則可連接無線耳機或手掣的轉插頭，或者有線遊戲裝置。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03561-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273621" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03561-1-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03561-1-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03561-1.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p>散熱設計延續了 PS5 的風格，機頂部分無散熱孔，減少積塵風險，但黑色外殼容易留下指紋。值得注意的是，PS5 Slim 的光碟機可與 PS5 Pro 共用，但另購的外殼無法兼容。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03576.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273623" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03576-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03576-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03576.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03598.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273625" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03598-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03598-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03598.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p>▲同 PS5 Pro Slim 一樣，主機燈光延續了 PS5 一</p><p>不過就我們所見，PS5 Pro 中央的位置都幾易積塵，特別是它黑色的表面，用家最好勤於打掃。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4075-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273622" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4075-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4075-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4075-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>散熱與噪音表現</h2><p>我們測試了初代 PS5 和 PS5 Pro 在玩《霍格華茲的傳承》30 分鐘後的温度。結果顯示兩者的散熱表現非常相似，PS5 Pro 的機背温度為 41.2℃，而 PS5 為 42.1℃，差異不大。只是用家較易接觸到的機頂，PS5 Pro 會較為涼快（PS5 Pro:21.4℃, PS5: 23℃)。噪音方面，我們在底噪 40.7 分貝的房間內進行測試，開機 30 分鐘之後 PS5 Pro 的機頂噪音為 42.7 分貝，機背為 45.9 分貝，而初代 PS5 機頂的 43.4 分貝以及 44.8 分貝。就同 Slim 版一樣，Pro 版構造令面向玩家一方的機頂會稍微安靜，反而玩家輕難聽到的機背噪音較大，結果就是玩家實際聽到的噪音較小。尤其是在一米的遊戲距離下，基本聽不到風扇聲音，夜晚的遊戲體驗不會被噪音打擾。</p><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td valign="top"></td><td valign="top">PS5 Pro</td><td valign="top">PS5</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">機頂噪音</td><td valign="top">42.7dB</td><td valign="top">43.4dB</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">機背噪音</td><td valign="top">45.9dB</td><td valign="top">44.8dB</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">機頂温度</td><td valign="top">21.4℃</td><td valign="top">23℃</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">機背温度</td><td valign="top">41.2℃</td><td valign="top">42.1℃</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">機面温度（下半部）</td><td valign="top">29.7℃</td><td valign="top">26.7℃</td></tr></tbody></table><p>機頂噪音：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03619.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273534" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03619-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03619-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03619.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲PS5 Pro: 42.7dB</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03628.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273535" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03628-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03628-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03628.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲PS5: 43.4dB</p><p>機背噪音：</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462574662_1223749832.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273531" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462574662_1223749832-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462574662_1223749832-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462574662_1223749832.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5 Pro: 45.9dB</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03629.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03629-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03629-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03629.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5: 44.8dB</p><p>機頂温度：</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462555496_1081753186.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273564" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462555496_1081753186-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462555496_1081753186-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462555496_1081753186.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5 Pro: 21.4℃</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462583258_1518197262.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273565" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462583258_1518197262-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462583258_1518197262-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462583258_1518197262.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5: 23℃</p><br /><b><ul><li>保真 <b>Pro </b>模式：此模式針對喜歡體驗新光追圖像效果的玩家，包括反射和陰影的增強。玩家可在畫質上探索全新的光影效果，城市景觀的細節和密度都顯著提高。</li><li>性能 <b>Pro </b>模式：針對 60 FPS 進行提升，透過 PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution (PSSR) 技術保留高畫質，同時啟用光線追蹤，並支援水面與窗户內部的反射效果，提供流暢且畫質優秀的體驗。</li></ul></li><li>光線追蹤增強：新增環境遮蔽與關鍵光影計算的光線追蹤，特別在遠距離景物中表現出色，為場景添加更為逼真的陰影和光線反射，提升了遊戲的沉浸感。</li></ul><figure id="attachment_1273361" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1273361" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273361" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110594117-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="ht